="1:30.230" end="1:30.400">の</span><span begin="1:30.400" end="1:30.550">な</span><span begin="1:30.550" end="1:30.750">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果低着头掩饰无法言喻的表情</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ienai hyoujou o utsumuku no nara</span></p><p begin="1:31.230" end="1:35.950" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:31.230" end="1:31.600">人</span><span begin="1:31.600" end="1:31.900">間</span><span begin="1:31.900" end="1:32.110">じゃ</span><span begin="1:32.110" end="1:32.310">な</span><span begin="1:32.310" end="1:32.440">い</span><span begin="1:32.440" end="1:32.630">っ</span><span begin="1:32.630" end="1:32.870">て</span><span begin="1:33.280" end="1:33.640">気</span><span begin="1:33.640" end="1:33.980">づ</span><span begin="1:33.980" end="1:34.340">い</span><span begin="1:34.340" end="1:34.660">て</span><span begin="1:34.660" end="1:35.010">い</span><span begin="1:35.010" end="1:35.240">た</span><span begin="1:35.240" end="1:35.530">ん</span><span begin="1:35.530" end="1:35.660">で</span><span begin="1:35.660" end="1:35.950">しょ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">其实你已经察觉到我不是人类了吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ningen janai tte kizuite itandesho</span></p><p begin="1:36.360" end="1:38.660" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:36.360" end="1:36.550">い</span><span begin="1:36.550" end="1:36.730">が</span><span begin="1:36.730" end="1:36.870">み</span><span begin="1:36.870" end="1:37.000">合</span><span begin="1:37.000" end="1:37.240">う</span><span begin="1:37.240" end="1:37.410">の</span><span begin="1:37.410" end="1:37.540">が</span><span begin="1:37.540" end="1:37.910">正</span><span begin="1:37.910" end="1:38.270">解</span><span begin="1:38.270" end="1:38.430">な</span><span begin="1:38.430" end="1:38.660">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果互相敌视才是正确答案的话</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Igamiau no ga seikai nara</span></p><p begin="1:39.050" end="1:42.190" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:39.050" end="1:39.270">そ</span><span begin="1:39.270" end="1:39.440">の</span><span begin="1:39.440" end="1:39.570">目</span><span begin="1:39.570" end="1:39.790">澄</span><span begin="1:39.790" end="1:39.920">ま</span><span begin="1:39.920" end="1:40.110">し</span><span begin="1:40.110" end="1:40.280">て</span><span begin="1:40.280" end="1:40.450">聞</span><span begin="1:40.450" end="1:40.820">き</span><span begin="1:40.920" end="1:41.640">連</span><span begin="1:41.640" end="1:41.740">ね</span><span begin="1:41.840" end="1:42.190">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就擦亮双眼倾听并罗列出来</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono me sumashite kikitsuranete</span></p><p begin="1:44.190" end="1:45.860" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:44.190" end="1:45.860">嗚呼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">啊啊</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa</span></p><p begin="1:46.750" end="1:49.530" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:46.750" end="1:47.110">痛</span><span begin="1:47.110" end="1:47.270">み</span><span begin="1:47.270" end="1:47.630">全</span><span begin="1:47.630" end="1:47.780">部</span><span begin="1:47.780" end="1:47.990">知</span><span begin="1:47.990" end="1:48.130">っ</span><span begin="1:48.130" end="1:48.300">て</span><span begin="1:48.300" end="1:48.690">空</span><span begin="1:48.690" end="1:48.800">を</span><span begin="1:48.800" end="1:49.150">仰</span><span begin="1:49.150" end="1:49.320">い</span><span begin="1:49.320" end="1:49.530">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">知晓全部的痛楚仰望天空</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itami zenbu shitte sora o aoide</span></p><p begin="1:49.810" end="1:51.740" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:49.810" end="1:49.980">そ</span><span begin="1:49.980" end="1:50.170">こ</span><span begin="1:50.170" end="1:50.340">か</span><span begin="1:50.340" end="1:50.490">ら</span><span begin="1:50.490" end="1:50.830">今</span><span begin="1:50.830" end="1:51.020">落</span><span begin="1:51.020" end="1:51.200">ち</span><span begin="1:51.200" end="1:51.330">る</span><span begin="1:51.330" end="1:51.560">ん</span><span begin="1:51.560" end="1:51.740">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在就要从那里坠落了</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Soko kara ima ochirunda</span></p><p begin="1:51.890" end="1:53.060" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:51.890" end="1:52.190">守</span><span begin="1:52.190" end="1:52.380">っ</span><span begin="1:52.380" end="1:52.530">て</span><span begin="1:52.530" end="1:52.730">く</span><span begin="1:52.730" end="1:52.870">れ</span><span begin="1:52.870" end="1:53.060">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">保护我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mamotte kure yo</span></p><p begin="1:53.240" end="1:54.360" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:53.240" end="1:53.420">磨</span><span begin="1:53.420" end="1:53.650">耗</span><span begin="1:53.650" end="1:53.930">し</span><span begin="1:53.930" end="1:54.120">て</span><span begin="1:54.120" end="1:54.230">る</span><span begin="1:54.230" end="1:54.360">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">正在磨损啊</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mamou shiteru yo</span></p><p begin="1:54.570" end="1:57.130" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:54.570" end="1:54.790">そ</span><span begin="1:54.790" end="1:54.960">の</span><span begin="1:54.960" end="1:55.280">電</span><span begin="1:55.280" end="1:55.350">波</span><span begin="1:55.350" end="1:55.460">思</span><span begin="1:55.460" end="1:55.800">考</span><span begin="1:55.800" end="1:55.960">に</span><span begin="1:55.960" end="1:56.140">既</span><span begin="1:56.140" end="1:56.460">読</span><span begin="1:56.460" end="1:56.650">を</span><span begin="1:56.650" end="1:56.830">つ</span><span begin="1:56.830" end="1:57.000">け</span><span begin="1:57.000" end="1:57.130">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">给那电波思考标上已读</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono denpa shikou ni kidoku o tsukete</span></p><p begin="1:57.300" end="1:59.730" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:57.300" end="1:57.510">そ</span><span begin="1:57.510" end="1:57.690">の</span><span begin="1:57.690" end="1:57.840">ま</span><span begin="1:57.840" end="1:58.030">ま</span><span begin="1:58.030" end="1:58.370">今</span><span begin="1:58.370" end="1:58.530">で</span><span begin="1:58.530" end="1:58.670">も</span><span begin="1:58.670" end="1:59.010">笑</span><span begin="1:59.010" end="1:59.210">っ</span><span begin="1:59.210" end="1:59.440">て</span><span begin="1:59.540" end="1:59.730">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就那样现在也笑一笑吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono mama ima demo waratte yo</span></p><p begin="2:00.060" end="2:02.580" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.060" end="2:00.370">脳</span><span begin="2:00.370" end="2:00.750">髄</span><span begin="2:00.750" end="2:00.890">を</span><span begin="2:00.890" end="2:01.070">混</span><span begin="2:01.070" end="2:01.250">ぜ</span><span begin="2:01.250" end="2:01.400">て</span><span begin="2:01.400" end="2:01.560">揺</span><span begin="2:01.560" end="2:01.930">さ</span><span begin="2:01.930" end="2:02.120">ぶ</span><span begin="2:02.120" end="2:02.270">っ</span><span begin="2:02.270" end="2:02.430">て</span><span begin="2:02.430" end="2:02.580">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">搅乱并摇撼脑髓吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nouzui o mazete yusabutte yo</span></p><p begin="2:02.810" end="2:03.960" itunes:key="L40" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:02.810" end="2:03.120">迷</span><span begin="2:03.120" end="2:03.290">っ</span><span begin="2:03.290" end="2:03.470">て</span><span begin="2:03.470" end="2:03.610">み</span><span begin="2:03.610" end="2:03.810">せ</span><span begin="2:03.810" end="2:03.960">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试着迷惘给我看</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mayotte misete</span></p><p begin="2:04.170" end="2:06.210" itunes:key="L41" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:04.170" end="2:04.500">届</span><span begin="2:04.500" end="2:04.670">い</span><span begin="2:04.670" end="2:04.840">て</span><span begin="2:04.840" end="2:04.980">み</span><span begin="2:04.980" end="2:05.420">せ</span><span begin="2:05.520" end="2:05.720">て</span><span begin="2:05.720" end="2:06.210">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试着传达给我看吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Todoite misete yo</span></p><p begin="2:17.120" end="2:19.690" itunes:key="L42" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:17.120" end="2:17.310">絵</span><span begin="2:17.310" end="2:17.440">文</span><span begin="2:17.440" end="2:17.630">字</span><span begin="2:17.630" end="2:17.780">ば</span><span begin="2:17.780" end="2:17.970">か</span><span begin="2:17.970" end="2:18.130">り</span><span begin="2:18.130" end="2:18.300">で</span><span begin="2:18.300" end="2:18.800">頷</span><span begin="2:18.800" end="2:18.980">き</span><span begin="2:18.980" end="2:19.160">あ</span><span begin="2:19.160" end="2:19.300">お</span><span begin="2:19.300" end="2:19.520">う</span><span begin="2:19.520" end="2:19.690">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就只用表情符号来互相点头附和吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Emoji bakari de unazukiaou yo</span></p><p begin="2:19.990" end="2:22.370" itunes:key="L43" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:19.990" end="2:20.160">上</span><span begin="2:20.160" end="2:20.360">昇</span><span begin="2:20.360" end="2:20.510">中</span><span begin="2:20.510" end="2:20.630">の</span><span begin="2:20.630" end="2:20.710">記</span><span begin="2:20.710" end="2:20.890">号</span><span begin="2:20.890" end="2:21.030">が</span><span begin="2:21.210" end="2:21.400">今</span><span begin="2:21.400" end="2:21.530">も</span><span begin="2:21.530" end="2:21.710">鼓</span><span begin="2:21.710" end="2:21.860">動</span><span begin="2:21.860" end="2:21.980">を</span><span begin="2:21.980" end="2:22.080">止</span><span begin="2:22.080" end="2:22.140">め</span><span begin="2:22.140" end="2:22.240">る</span><span begin="2:22.240" end="2:22.370">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">正在上升的符号如今心也停止跳动了吗</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Joushou chuu no kigou ga ima mo kodou o tomeru no</span></p><p begin="2:22.710" end="2:24.950" itunes:key="L44" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:22.710" end="2:23.090">単</span><span begin="2:23.090" end="2:23.420">純</span><span begin="2:23.420" end="2:23.590">だ</span><span begin="2:23.590" end="2:23.750">と</span><span begin="2:23.750" end="2:23.940">か</span><span begin="2:23.940" end="2:24.060">言</span><span begin="2:24.060" end="2:24.190">う</span><span begin="2:24.290" end="2:24.450">の</span><span begin="2:24.450" end="2:24.610">な</span><span begin="2:24.610" end="2:24.950">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果你要说这很简单的话</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tanjun da toka iu no nara</span></p><p begin="2:25.280" end="2:27.830" itunes:key="L45" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:25.280" end="2:25.450">い</span><span begin="2:25.450" end="2:25.590">ま</span><span begin="2:25.590" end="2:25.790">す</span><span begin="2:25.790" end="2:25.920">ぐ</span><span begin="2:25.920" end="2:26.150">わ</span><span begin="2:26.150" end="2:26.310">か</span><span begin="2:26.310" end="2:26.470">り</span><span begin="2:26.470" end="2:26.640">や</span><span begin="2:26.640" end="2:26.840">す</span><span begin="2:26.840" end="2:26.910">く</span><span begin="2:26.910" end="2:27.300">教</span><span begin="2:27.300" end="2:27.510">え</span><span begin="2:27.510" end="2:27.660">て</span><span begin="2:27.660" end="2:27.830">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在立刻浅显易懂地告诉我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ima sugu wakariyasuku oshiete yo</span></p><p begin="2:28.150" end="2:30.280" itunes:key="L46" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:28.150" end="2:28.510">寂</span><span begin="2:28.510" end="2:28.690">し</span><span begin="2:28.690" end="2:28.890">く</span><span begin="2:28.890" end="2:29.020">な</span><span begin="2:29.020" end="2:29.190">い</span><span begin="2:29.190" end="2:29.340">よ</span><span begin="2:29.340" end="2:29.660">今</span><span begin="2:29.660" end="2:29.990">更</span><span begin="2:30.100" end="2:30.280">もう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">已经不寂寞了哦 事到如今</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sabishikunai yo imasara mou</span></p><p begin="2:30.750" end="2:32.970" itunes:key="L47" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:30.750" end="2:30.910">い</span><span begin="2:30.910" end="2:31.070">つ</span><span begin="2:31.070" end="2:31.270">で</span><span begin="2:31.270" end="2:31.410">も</span><span begin="2:31.410" end="2:31.760">繋</span><span begin="2:31.760" end="2:31.910">が</span><span begin="2:31.910" end="2:32.100">っ</span><span begin="2:32.100" end="2:32.280">て</span><span begin="2:32.280" end="2:32.420">る</span><span begin="2:32.420" end="2:32.610">ん</span><span begin="2:32.610" end="2:32.800">だ</span><span begin="2:32.800" end="2:32.970">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无论何时都紧紧相连着哦</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsudemo tsunagatterunda yo</span></p><p begin="2:33.140" end="2:38.410" itunes:key="L48" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:33.140" end="2:33.310">だ</span><span begin="2:33.310" end="2:33.460">か</span><span begin="2:33.460" end="2:33.570">ら</span><span begin="2:33.690" end="2:33.840">も</span><span begin="2:33.840" end="2:33.990">う</span><span begin="2:35.860" end="2:36.040">テ</span><span begin="2:36.040" end="2:36.200">レ</span><span begin="2:36.200" end="2:36.370">パ</span><span begin="2:36.370" end="2:36.710">シー</span><span begin="2:36.710" end="2:36.860">に</span><span begin="2:36.860" end="2:37.030">気</span><span begin="2:37.030" end="2:37.180">づ</span><span begin="2:37.180" end="2:37.380">い</span><span begin="2:37.380" end="2:37.540">た</span><span begin="2:37.540" end="2:37.740">振</span><span begin="2:37.740" end="2:37.900">り</span><span begin="2:37.900" end="2:38.050">し</span><span begin="2:38.050" end="2:38.250">て</span><span begin="2:38.250" end="2:38.410">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">所以就装作已经察觉到了心灵感应吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dakara mou terepashii ni kizuita furi shite yo</span></p><p begin="2:38.550" end="2:41.360" itunes:key="L49" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:38.550" end="2:38.790">そ</span><span begin="2:38.790" end="2:38.940">の</span><span begin="2:38.940" end="2:39.100">目</span><span begin="2:39.100" end="2:39.270">か</span><span begin="2:39.270" end="2:39.430">っ</span><span begin="2:39.430" end="2:39.620">ぽ</span><span begin="2:39.620" end="2:39.790">じ</span><span begin="2:39.790" end="2:39.950">っ</span><span begin="2:39.950" end="2:40.110">て</span><span begin="2:40.110" end="2:40.270">気</span><span begin="2:40.270" end="2:40.620">づ</span><span begin="2:40.620" end="2:40.810">い</span><span begin="2:40.810" end="2:40.980">た</span><span begin="2:40.980" end="2:41.360">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果你睁大眼睛察觉到了的话</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono me kappojitte kizuitara</span></p><p begin="2:41.650" end="2:44.860" itunes:key="L50" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:41.650" end="2:42.180">心</span><span begin="2:42.180" end="2:42.300">の</span><span begin="2:42.300" end="2:42.620">内</span><span begin="2:42.620" end="2:42.790">を</span><span begin="2:42.790" end="2:43.120">荒</span><span begin="2:43.120" end="2:43.360">ん</span><span begin="2:43.360" end="2:43.470">で</span><span begin="2:43.700" end="2:44.020">送</span><span begin="2:44.020" end="2:44.220">っ</span><span begin="2:44.220" end="2:44.360">て</span><span begin="2:44.360" end="2:44.550">み</span><span begin="2:44.550" end="2:44.710">て</span><span begin="2:44.710" end="2:44.860">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就试着将这荒芜的内心发送过来吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kokoro no uchi o susande okutte mite yo</span></p><p begin="2:45.060" end="2:46.230" itunes:key="L51" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:45.060" end="2:45.230">飛</span><span begin="2:45.230" end="2:45.450">ば</span><span begin="2:45.450" end="2:45.580">し</span><span begin="2:45.580" end="2:45.740">て</span><span begin="2:45.740" end="2:45.910">み</span><span begin="2:45.910" end="2:46.070">て</span><span begin="2:46.070" end="2:46.230">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试着让它飞翔吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tobashite mite yo</span></p><p begin="2:46.390" end="2:48.930" itunes:key="L52" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:46.390" end="2:46.600">そ</span><span begin="2:46.600" end="2:46.780">の</span><span begin="2:46.780" end="2:47.100">電</span><span begin="2:47.100" end="2:47.180">波</span><span begin="2:47.180" end="2:47.260">思</span><span begin="2:47.260" end="2:47.630">考</span><span begin="2:47.630" end="2:47.750">で</span><span begin="2:47.750" end="2:48.180">叫</span><span begin="2:48.180" end="2:48.310">ん</span><span begin="2:48.310" end="2:48.480">で</span><span begin="2:48.480" end="2:48.650">み</span><span begin="2:48.650" end="2:48.780">て</span><span begin="2:48.780" end="2:48.930">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试着用那电波思考呼喊吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono denpa shikou de sakende mite yo</span></p><p begin="2:49.170" end="2:51.550" itunes:key="L53" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:49.170" end="2:49.330">で</span><span begin="2:49.330" end="2:49.500">き</span><span begin="2:49.500" end="2:49.650">る</span><span begin="2:49.650" end="2:49.840">な</span><span begin="2:49.840" end="2:50.000">ら</span><span begin="2:50.000" end="2:50.360">今</span><span begin="2:50.360" end="2:50.500">も</span><span begin="2:50.500" end="2:50.850">笑</span><span begin="2:50.850" end="2:51.030">っ</span><span begin="2:51.030" end="2:51.370">て</span><span begin="2:51.370" end="2:51.550">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果可以的话现在也笑一笑吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dekiru nara ima mo waratte yo</span></p><p begin="2:51.870" end="2:54.400" itunes:key="L54" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:51.870" end="2:52.080">で</span><span begin="2:52.080" end="2:52.210">も</span><span begin="2:52.210" end="2:52.530">今</span><span begin="2:5