40">染</span><span begin="3:00.940" end="3:01.100">ま</span><span begin="3:01.100" end="3:01.250">っ</span><span begin="3:01.250" end="3:01.410">て</span><span begin="3:01.410" end="3:01.590">ゆ</span><span begin="3:01.590" end="3:01.730">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">爱与哀与相逢 如今都染上了湛蓝</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ai o ai o ai o ai ni ima wa somatte yuku</span></p><p begin="3:02.100" end="3:03.150" itunes:key="L58" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:02.100" end="3:02.270">焦</span><span begin="3:02.270" end="3:02.450">が</span><span begin="3:02.450" end="3:02.620">し</span><span begin="3:02.620" end="3:02.780">て</span><span begin="3:02.780" end="3:02.970">ゆ</span><span begin="3:02.970" end="3:03.150">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">渐渐焦灼</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kogashite yuku</span></p><p begin="3:03.420" end="3:05.800" itunes:key="L59" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:03.420" end="3:03.630">そ</span><span begin="3:03.630" end="3:03.800">の</span><span begin="3:03.800" end="3:03.980">記</span><span begin="3:03.980" end="3:04.320">号</span><span begin="3:04.320" end="3:04.490">で</span><span begin="3:04.490" end="3:04.830">今</span><span begin="3:04.830" end="3:05.170">綴</span><span begin="3:05.170" end="3:05.350">っ</span><span begin="3:05.350" end="3:05.540">て</span><span begin="3:05.540" end="3:05.800">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在就用那符号拼凑吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono kigou de ima tsuzutte yo</span></p><p begin="3:06.200" end="3:14.470" itunes:key="L60" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:06.200" end="3:06.530">何</span><span begin="3:06.530" end="3:06.700">も</span><span begin="3:06.700" end="3:06.900">か</span><span begin="3:06.900" end="3:07.050">も</span><span begin="3:07.050" end="3:07.400">全</span><span begin="3:07.400" end="3:07.560">部</span><span begin="3:07.560" end="3:07.890">届</span><span begin="3:07.890" end="3:07.980">い</span><span begin="3:08.410" end="3:09.110">て</span><span begin="3:09.110"